project_abstract.cdata: The Highway Engineering Project includes the detailed engineering of the two roads which link Lahore with Lyallpur and Sheikhupura with Khushab will include among others, site investigations, topographic surveys, detailed designs, the preparation of bills of quantities, bidding documents, schedules of construction work and cost estimates. The Highway Engineering Project includes the detailed engineering of the bridges across the Chenab and Jhelum rivers on the route of the Sheikhupura-Khushab highway will be undertaken by the staff of the Province of West Pakistan and will be reviewed by the consultants.
